# Chakra UI

- Use **Chakra UI** (`@chakra-ui/react`) for all newly created components and pages.
- Prefer Chakra primitives: `Box`, `Flex`, `Text`, `Heading`, `Link`, `Button`, `Image`, `List`, etc.
- Use Chakra style props (`color`, `bg`, `p`, `m`, `fontSize`, `_hover`, etc.) instead of custom CSS or CSS modules when possible.
- For layout: use `Box`, `Flex`, `Grid`; for typography: `Text`, `Heading`; for links: `Link` with `as={RouterLink}` for React Router.
- Keep custom CSS only for complex cases (e.g. hero full-bleed breakout, keyframe animations) and use CSS modules only when Chakra cannot cover the need.
